title: Cookies/Private Browsing
content:
In the past month or so, I have noticed that sites I visit in private mode will occasionally leave cookies that are visible when I check "manage cookies and site data." In all cases, these are sites I entered by right clicking on a link or bookmark and choosing "open in new private window."

What's up?
creator: hobro1

title: Password
content: After clean a history passwords was reset.
